2011-10-14  Alexander Grein <ag@typo3-webagentur.com>

	* Remove some placeholder, size and maxlength attributes from element which are not allowed in HTML5.
	* Add constant to switch off the automatic scrolling to field with first validation error.
	* Add constants (and functions of course) to enable trigger icons for date and date time fields.
	* Add function to add link to uploads in recipient emails.
	* Add function to use form title as uploads subfolder name.
	* Remove "hard coded" novalidate="novalidate" attribute from tmpl_formwrap.html form tag to allow "real" HTML5 validation, if constant "plugin.powermail.js.validation" is set to 0.
	* Improvement of the javascript validation for multiple pages forms (client site). Tab with first error is activated automatically now.
	* Fix for select validation: only required select field will be validated now.
	* Improvement of the javascript validation for radio buttons: No more double validation errors if more than one mandatory radio groups are in a form.
	* Better error messages for multiple select fields and checkboxes.
	* Reorganisation of all constant parameters.
	* Add some new parameters to adjust by typoscript/constants: position of error messages, offset of error messages, tags used by error message generation, single error (show only one error at the same time).
	* Changed "Save to db" logic:  If no page-select in plugin setting "Save powermails to page" (or over the "PID.dblog" constant), NO data storage anymore.
	* If the backend module and data storing is disabled in the extension setting (over the extension manager), no more "Save powermails to page" is shown in the plugin settings and NO data storage anymore.
	* Add updater script for empty powermail page storage settings to easily switch from powermail 1.6.4 to 1.6.5 or higher.
	* Improvements for date, datetime and checkbox fields to work (basically) without javascript.
	* All hidden fields needed by field types checkbox, date, datetime which where formerly hardcoded in "tmpl_fieldwrap.html", will now be generated by javascript (query) defined in tmpl_frontend.js.
	* To store date and datetime inputs, also if a user has switched off javascript, a corresponding switch was included in the main typescript.
	* Basic CSS Code optimization for better fit in introduction package layout.
	* Add powermail_frontend_basic.less file for generating powermail_frontend_basic.css using less.app.
	* Add new country zone selector, uses jQuery and eID instead of xajax.
	* Add scheduler task to import csv data to powermail
	* Add server side validation for digits, alpha, alphanum, alpha with umlauts and alphanum with umlauts
	* Changed description icon from image-tag to span with background image.
	* Add constant to define error message css class
	* Add Hook in export class to change tsconfig dynamically
	* Fixes a bug which won't allow a XLS download to start in IE with SSL on
	* Exchanged captcha image and input field position in tmpl_fieldwrap.html Template
	* CSS improvements for wt_captcha integration

